---
title: Cheesy Monterey Double Beef Jack Burgers with Garlic and Rosemary Sweet Potatoes
description: Grab the cooler and get ready to hit the grill! Delight your tastebuds with this Monterey Jack and fig topped rosemary burger. An elegant side of garlic rosemary sweet potatoes rounds out this summer weekend winner!
